query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 u1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 1 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('16.04',
'algebraic-topology',
'commutative-algebra',
'complex-numbers',
'continuity',
'definite-integrals',
'diophantine-equations',
'elementary-set-theory',
'indefinite-integrals',
'nvidia',
'pde',
'vector-spaces')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Deputy',
'Disciplined',
'Favorite Question',
'Generalist',
'Tag Editor',
'Tenacious')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
